# Smart Heart Assistant — Full Project Documentation

---

## 1. Project Overview

This project is a **Flask-based conversational chatbot** that guides Arabic-speaking users through a structured medical intake questionnaire focused on **heart health**. At the end of the conversation, it generates personalized cardiovascular advice, saves the collected patient data as a JSON report, and instantly relays the findings to a primary Java Spring Boot backend database.

### Core Idea

Instead of filling out a boring medical form, the patient chats with a friendly bot in Arabic. The bot asks questions one-by-one across 7 stages (greeting → demographics → lifestyle → medical history → symptoms), validates answers in real-time, and finishes with a tailored health summary securely linked to a concurrent session.

