## 6. How to Run

```bash
# 1. Create virtual environment
python -m venv .venv

# 2. Activate it (Windows)
.venv\Scripts\activate

# 3. Setup Env and install deps
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 4. Run the web server
python app.py
# → Open http://localhost:5000
```

